{"word":"ἐκτελέω","slug":"ἐκτελέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκτελέω</b></el> <el>(epic <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a> <el>ἐξετέλειον</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-τελέσω</el>) </el><p/><i>to bring quite to an end, to accomplish, achieve</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>ἐκτελέεσθαι</el>, <i>to be accomplished</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/>"}]}